name: GUEST IN HOUSE
query:
Select
  `tabHMS Reservation`.name as "Reservation:Link/HMS Reservation:120",
  `tabHMS Reservation`.status as "Status:Select/Status:100",
  `tabHMS Reservation`.customer_id as "Customer:Link/Customer:200",
  `tabHMS Reservation`.actual_room_id as "Room:Link/HMS Room:100",
  `tabHMS Reservation`.room_type as "Room Type:Data:100",
  `tabHMS Reservation`.arrival as "Arrival:Datetime:150",
  `tabHMS Reservation`.departure as "Departure:Datetime:120",
  `tabCustomer`.mobile_no as "Phone:Data:150"
From
   `tabHMS Reservation` Join `tabCustomer` on `tabHMS Reservation`.customer_id = `tabCustomer`.name
